    <title>The Cost of Name Changes</title>
    <link>https://forum.throneoflies.com/t/the-cost-of-name-changes/3623</link>
    <description>As it stands, it&#39;s free to change your username in ToL.

Okay, yes I hate how ToS charges you $5 IRL to change your username, but it&#39;s not just a moneygrab reason- well, not entirely. When you give people the ability to change their usernames, unlimited- for free, you open the gateways to massive nametrolling.

Anyways, my idea is simple,
make Name Changes cost a little bit of GP, even if not much- say like 250, or even 100 GP per name change. Just something.</description>
    
